data.title: La Joie de Vivre (1969)
data.meta_description: La Joie de Vivre: Directed by Norodom Sihanouk. With Nhiek Tioulong, Sieng Dy, Kon Samoeun, Sisowath Kantanavong. Captain Siporak and Inspector Sam Baun raid the gambling place at Kirirom owned by Prince Chantavong. This place is disguised as an orchid shop. As soon as Prince Chantavong is detained in jail, his wife, princess Sulpra, spends her time having a love relationship with her nephew. Then she meets Okhnia Sneha Sambat, a great hotelier. Okhnia takes her to a big island at Sihanoukville for their holiday. After being released from prison, Prince Chantavong, armed with guns, tries to look for her everywhere.
